# The Dead Partner · the grief Don runs from

a synth of the GDS (The Goods: Live Hard, Sell Hard, 2009) film-world — emergence: spiritual. moniker ⟦The Dead Partner:GDS:c229c1⟧

**synth —** no single User; a parabolic trope of the film distilled.

**who —** The Dead Partner — Craig McDermott (a Will Ferrell cameo), Don's late colleague who dies because Don packed sex toys instead of a parachute.
**what —** The wound under the hustle: the recklessness and grief the rootless man is outrunning, played as a cameo gag with a real ache beneath.
